---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="-mt-12 sm:mt-0">
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-6">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-medium text-center bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-[#c4a7e7] via-[#ea9a97] to-[#eb6f92] sm:text-4xl">
         blursed 
        </h1><svg class="text-3xl text-rose-300" stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M573.7 252.5C422.5 197.4 201.3 96.7 201.3 96.7c-15.7-4.1-17.9 11.1-17.9 11.1-5 61.1 33.6 160.5 53.6 182.8 19.9 22.3 319.1 113.7 319.1 113.7S326 357.9 270.5 341.9c-55.6-16-37.9 17.8-37.9 17.8 11.4 61.7 64.9 131.8 107.2 138.4 42.2 6.6 220.1 4 220.1 4s-35.5 4.1-93.2 11.9c-42.7 5.8-97 12.5-111.1 17.8-33.1 12.5 24 62.6 24 62.6 84.7 76.8 129.7 50.5 129.7 50.5 33.3-10.7 61.4-18.5 85.2-24.2L565 743.1h84.6L603 928l205.3-271.9H700.8l22.3-38.7c.3.5.4.8.4.8S799.8 496.1 829 433.8l.6-1h-.1c5-10.8 8.6-19.7 10-25.8 17-71.3-114.5-99.4-265.8-154.5z"></path></svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-7 text-xl text-rose-100/90 sm:mt-9">
      Somos uma organização sem fundos lucrativos criada por dois estudantes da <a class="text-indigo-400 hover:underline" href="https://epmontijo.edu.pt/">Escola Profissional do Montijo</a> que constroi PWAs <i>(Progressive Web Apps)</i> com foco na segurança e privacidade.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-7 text-xl text-rose-100/90 sm:mt-9">
      Pode contactar-nos em <a
        href="mailto:contact@blursed.org"
        class="hover:underline hover:decoration-rose-300/30 hover:underline-offset-2 hover:text-rose-200/90 focus:outline-none focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-rose-500/70 text-gray-500"
        >[contact@blursed.org]</a
      >
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4 sm:mt-6">
      <div
        class="flex items-center space-x-7 text-base font-semibold leading-none text-rose-100/90"
      >
        <a
          href="https://github.com/d6stiny"
          class="group focus:outline-none focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-rose-500/70"
        >
          <div class="sm:flex sm:items-center sm:space-x-2">
            <div class="mb-1.5 flex justify-center sm:mb-0 sm:block">
              <div
                class="rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-tl from-purple-500/80 to-rose-400/80 p-1 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:scale-[1.2] group-hover:rounded-[10px] group-hover:shadow-purple-500/40 group-active:translate-y-1"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  class="w-[18px] transform text-rose-100 transition delay-100 duration-500 ease-out group-hover:scale-110"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                >
                  <path
                    d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"
                  ></path>
                  <path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>GitHub</div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://www.twitch.tv/d6stinylol"
          class="group focus:outline-none focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-rose-500/70"
        >
          <div class="sm:flex sm:items-center sm:space-x-2">
            <div class="mb-1.5 flex justify-center sm:mb-0 sm:block">
              <div
                class="rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-tl from-purple-500/80 to-rose-400/80 p-1 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:scale-[1.2] group-hover:rounded-[10px] group-hover:shadow-purple-500/40 group-active:translate-y-1"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  class="w-[18px] transform text-rose-100 transition delay-100 duration-500 ease-out group-hover:scale-110"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                >
                  <path d="M21 2H3v16h5v4l4-4h5l4-4V2zm-10 9V7m5 4V7"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>Twitch</div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/d6stinylol/"
          class="group focus:outline-none focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-rose-500/70"
        >
          <div class="sm:flex sm:items-center sm:space-x-2">
            <div class="mb-1.5 flex justify-center sm:mb-0 sm:block">
              <div
                class="rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-tl from-purple-500/80 to-rose-400/80 p-1 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:scale-[1.2] group-hover:rounded-[10px] group-hover:shadow-purple-500/40 group-active:translate-y-1"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  class="w-[18px] transform text-rose-100 transition delay-100 duration-500 ease-out group-hover:scale-110"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                >
                  <rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"></rect>
                  <path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"
                  ></path>
                  <line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"></line>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>Instagram</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-5 mt-14 sm:mt-32 mb-14">
      <section id="projects">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-rose-100/80 sm:text-4xl">
         Produtos 
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xl text-rose-100/90 sm:mt-6">
          O projeto no qual estamos focados atualmente é <a
            href="https://github.com/d6stiny/pap"
            class="hover:underline hover:decoration-rose-300/30 hover:underline-offset-2 hover:text-rose-200/90 focus:outline-none focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-rose-500/70 text-gray-500"
            >[GradChat]</a
          >, um chat semi-formal, privado e seguro. Estamos também a trabalhar passivamente <a
            href="https://github.com/d6stiny/pap"
            class="hover:underline hover:decoration-rose-300/30 hover:underline-offset-2 hover:text-rose-200/90 focus:outline-none focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-rose-500/70 text-gray-500"
            >[CashControl]</a
          >, uma plataforma de gestão de finanças, privada, segura e fácil de usar.

          <br>
          Ambos estarão posteriormente abertos para contribuições open-source!
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-rose-100/90 sm:mt-6">
          Para construir os nossos projetos utilizamos TypeScript para o backend e Next.js para o frontend.
        </p>
      </section>

       <section id="aboutme">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-rose-100/80 sm:text-4xl">
         Sobre mim
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xl text-rose-100/90 sm:mt-6">
          Eu, Diogo Castro, CEO da blursed.org, sou programador backend auto-didata desde os 9 anos. Sou criador de conteúdo na Twitch estou neste momento a acabar o curso de Gestão e Programação de Sistemas Informáticos.
          <br>
          A blursed foi criada com o intuito de fornecer aos utilizadores uma alternativa aos produtos já existentes que violam constantemente a nossa privacidade e segurança. Será o projeto base para apresentação da minha PAP em Gestão e Programação de Sistemas Informáticos.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
